      description : "TCAT-AS-000050 - AccessLogValve must be configured for each application context."
      info        : "Tomcat has the ability to host multiple contexts (applications) on one physical server by using the <Host><Context> attribute. This allows the admin to specify audit log settings on a per application basis.

